      "text": "Before I could speak, a woman whispered, 'Don’t turn around.'"
    },
    {
      "startSeconds": 21.072,
      "endSeconds": 25.272,
      "text": "My stomach dropped. I froze."
    },
    {
      "startSeconds": 25.272,
      "endSeconds": 32.424,
      "text": "Then I heard it. Footsteps behind me. Slow. One step. Then another."
    },
    {
      "startSeconds": 32.424,
      "endSeconds": 39.072,
      "text": "The woman on the phone started crying. 'Please,' she said. 'He already has my son.'"
    },
    {
      "startSeconds": 39.072,
      "endSeconds": 40.488,
      "text": "I turned anyway."
    },
    {
      "startSeconds": 40.488,
      "endSeconds": 49.488,
      "text": "And standing under the only broken streetlight... was a little boy. Holding my exact same phone. And it was ringing too."
    }
